Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是梅札蘭斯的紋章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.04,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於找到了 傳說中的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.96,0:00:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.06,0:00:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.75,0:00:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.91,0:00:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.73,0:00:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.71,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一唱 天空與風之歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.84,0:02:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發現目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航向東北1時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偏轉45度方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本酷德·望·朱魯愛特大爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼疼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還嫩著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別礙手礙腳的...一邊待著去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.56,0:03:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說什麼 我可是能熟練自如地操縱小型艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不說這個 也給我弄件兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光在一邊看太沒勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切 來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞什麼 和民航機不配嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在黑暗之國...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 對了 橫行 是橫行來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,橫行於黑暗之國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洋洋得意的鼠輩們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來帶走你們秘藏寶物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.07,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風之空盜團紅山貓降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開場白太長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想踩到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,磨磨蹭蹭地在幹什麼 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,工作結束了 撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.69,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 別丟下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫酷 紅山貓的下任老大就是本大爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.71,0:05:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被搶走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追 然後搶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是這個世界最珍貴的寶物之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我威風凌凌地教訓道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.60,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們就算像溝鼠一樣能逃避奉納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也休想逃過我紅山貓的指間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後那傢伙嚇得渾身發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 多麼厲害的大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請和首領美言幾句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留我一條狗命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於是我就很紳士地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 知道了 別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不會對沒反抗能力的人下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.66,0:05:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過一個水手 得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些話等到能穩穩當當地開飛艇後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,半吊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思啊 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駕駛飛艇之類的我不是都幹過好多次了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 酷 那說不上駕駛 是直衝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.16,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過那也實在是差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.97,0:06:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每次會怎麼引人發笑真是很期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.42,0:06:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總是鬧出超乎預想的笑話 感激不盡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切 大家都把我當白癡看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.94,0:06:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要是認真起來開飛船什麼的還不是小菜一碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然也有幾次筆直地飛不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.99,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,東碰西撞地弄得頭上滿是包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.53,0:06:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不小心駕駛小型艇撞上飛空艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,衝撞 起包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,衝撞 起包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,衝撞 起包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,衝撞 起包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回憶個屁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 寶物庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 我還未看過今天的戰利品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先進來瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪的東西也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好髒的箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我眼花了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 確實好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個 這個 這個 再這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女...女孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能吧 一定是人偶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過...好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 被什麼迷住了 人偶啊 人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 難得看到就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,睫毛好長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮膚也好白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 好像很柔軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 為為...為什麼人偶會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你...你不是人偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是稍微減減速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 好不容易知道在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,錯過的話也許就再也收不回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以...加速...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個...我說...你活著的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.05,0:09:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會在那個箱子裏 待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是...要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 對...對...對...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.28,0:10:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.74,0:10:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你散發著人的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 我討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說什麼散發著人的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 敵襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有艘小型艇飛過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別被打下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙什麼來頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒看到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,機動力也不一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.08,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.94,0:11:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大 不會是空軍來抓我們了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.22,0:11:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋 一幫膽小怕死的窩囊廢怎麼可能就派一架過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,襲擊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去吊艙那裏待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就讓我開小型艇去迎擊 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.26,0:11:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋 緊急關頭還泡妞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弄錯了 這是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.20,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請求著陸的信號 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.22,0:11:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同意著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以禮相待但別掉以輕心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快 打開艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.83,0:12:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 把人帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.88,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.37,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好 這麼早來打擾真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是煌珠完全保護協會——守護翼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全保護協會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.22,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 我們是來要回之前被你們空盜團搶走的煌珠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.46,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然看起來像個可愛的美少女我可是個傑出的成熟女性哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這個隊的隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫龍威 副隊長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫奇雅 肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什麼啊 那個聖戰...什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.56,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是就在你身後嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.96,0:13:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 仔細想想怎麼會甦醒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒幹過什麼嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,動手動腳了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有幹什麼見不得人的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒干 什麼都沒干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把真話說出來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.49,0:13:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我正餓著呢還是不要惹我發火的為好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說這孩子就是煌珠 是真的嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 那是當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖戰什麼的 知道嗎 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.14,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 跟人同契戰鬥的傳言倒是有聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戰鬥...這孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微有些不同之處 但差不多就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.47,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之我們天使守衛隊長久以來就在尋找她的蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.56,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子在煌珠中也是響噹噹的七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼能讓她與你們這些垃圾為伍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,獅子芳香樹 七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,支柱呱呱樹 七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七步穗樹 啊 受不了 是七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七煌寶樹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,錯了 七煌寶樹 嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 行了 先不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底你們想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣滿意嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上回扣無須交稅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把這艘飛船整個翻新一下還會有的多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,5千萬G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.08,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,5千...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我安靜點 你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為雖說是偷來的但總算那孩子是你們的戰利品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且錢能解決問題的話就再好不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 你說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直說行嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別開玩笑了 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不滿意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 你可真會討價還價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 這樣如何 不能再高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虧本大出血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得我們一番好意...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都說了 別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們把這女孩當成什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.88,0:15:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,錯 那個聖戰什麼的不也是和我們一樣的人類嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.94,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 與我們守護者也就是人類是不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為那樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為那樣就可以把這女孩像貨物一樣交易嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說了 是謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幫忙找到這女孩的謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼說的話可以接受嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.35,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝禮...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.25,0:16:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.01,0:16:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管理由是什麼 不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管你出多少錢都不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要動手嗎 終於要動手了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 前輩 這裏還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雙方互相作出讓步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.53,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們就能得到一大筆錢飛船也可以整個翻新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也順利完成任務順利升職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有那麼和平的解決方式卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話只能使出殺手鑭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的是 快速解決 快點去吃東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想幹什麼 殺手鑭什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武力行使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.72,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.75,0:16:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就如剛才所說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們一夥的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弟兄們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you 老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要用這個保護那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽好 一定要保護好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.11,0:17:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍威 奇雅 其他的交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 同契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微等等 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏同契的話後果會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.00,0:18:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呦 快點搞定吧 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別太興奮了 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武器 生成了武器！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打得很辛苦嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我若保護好了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能把她交給我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給你？ 多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是這份人情可要好好償還啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會吧 怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,口氣不是挺大的嘛 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是沒辦法的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.45,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事 幹嘛你們都追著那女孩不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道就因為煌珠什麼的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她也不想和人有所瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.76,0:19:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠是不能和人攪在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你散發著人的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾經孤身一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出生後不久就成了孤兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是老大收留不知會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這女孩也一樣 孤身一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.87,0:20:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知怎的 感覺和以前的我一樣孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想讓她獨自一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.43,0:20:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是想更理解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.95,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.10,0:20:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是人 但和別人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和別人不同 因為和別人不一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請等一下 一旦同契的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牽引之線{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此傾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追及之畏{\a6}
